{
  "stem": "13584.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I cannot-- it was-- he was a Christian, a leader of the village, a Pole.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was Niewiadomski, and I-- I wanted to mention his name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was like a sheriff in the [? house. ?] Before, when Germans entered Poland and start to approach those areas, he decide to rescue the Jews of this village.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were nine Jews in this village, nine souls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He prepared in a cellar, under the barn, a hiding place for those Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said to them, apparently, during the day, don't you even say a word.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "During the night, whisper if you want to communicate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody knows how long will the war last.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I know it's a horrible time for the Jews, and I [? want-- ?] you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course, they [? were-- ?] thank you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "For no-- just for human reasons, for human reasons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This sheriff-- I'll call him sheriff-- Sheriff Niewiadomski, had two kids, a son, adult, and a daughter, an adult.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The son was in the partisans, in the guerrilla war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "His son-- his son was in the nearby woods fighting the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "His daughter cooperated with the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the father, Niewiadomski, knew about her-- about-- about her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was winter, 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was exactly maybe few months before liberation by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said, I think I heard human voices, a human cough.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to the Gestapo, and I'm going to tell them to search if you have Jews here or whoever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, he said, go ahead and tell them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As soon as she took her horse-- horse to ride to the Gestapo, he took another horse, apparently, and ran to the woods to his son.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came to the woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He told his son.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
